{"thig5.3:0.1":"Therigatha 5.3 ","thig5.3:0.2":"Pancakanipata ","thig5.3:0.3":"Sihatherigatha ","thig5.3:1.1":"“Ayoniso manasikara, ","thig5.3:1.2":"kamaragena attita; ","thig5.3:1.3":"Ahosim uddhata pubbe, ","thig5.3:1.4":"citte avasavattini. ","thig5.3:2.1":"Pariyutthita klesehi, ","thig5.3:2.2":"subhasannanuvattini; ","thig5.3:2.3":"Samam cittassa na labhim, ","thig5.3:2.4":"ragacittavasanuga. ","thig5.3:3.1":"Kisa pandu vivanna ca, ","thig5.3:3.2":"satta vassani cariham; ","thig5.3:3.3":"Naham diva va rattim va, ","thig5.3:3.4":"sukham vindim sudukkhita. ","thig5.3:4.1":"Tato rajjum gahetvana, ","thig5.3:4.2":"pavisim vanamantaram; ","thig5.3:4.3":"Varam me idha ubbandham, ","thig5.3:4.4":"yanca hinam punacare. ","thig5.3:5.1":"Dalhapasam karitvana, ","thig5.3:5.2":"rukkhasakhaya bandhiya; ","thig5.3:5.3":"Pakkhipim pasam givayam, ","thig5.3:5.4":"atha cittam vimucci me”ti. ","thig5.3:6.1":"… Siha theri …. "}